{% from "components/buttons.njk" import startButton %}
{% from "components/print-button/macro.njk" import printButton %}
{% from "components/form-header/macro.njk" import formHeader with context %}
{% from "../views/view-helpers.njk" import questionsPreview %}

{% extends "layouts/main.njk" %}
{% set bodyClass = 'has-static-header' %}

{% block content %}
    <main role="main" id="content">
        <div class="content-box u-inner-wide-only accent--{{ pageAccent }} a--border-top">
            {{ formHeader(
                title = title,
                suffix = copy.description | safe
            ) }}

            <div class="u-constrained-wide s-prose accent-content--{{ pageAccent }}">
                <p>The Government is investing up to Â£1.2 million from dormant bank and building society accounts in three areas to develop the capacity of local, frontline grassroots organisations who help young people who are facing barriers to work.
                <a href="/funding/programmes/youth-capacity-fund">View full programme details</a>.</p>

                {{ startButton(startUrl) }}

                <p>Organisations and community groups are invited to tell us about their current work and ideas for development using this simple online form, which contains three key questions and some additional information. Please read the <a href="/funding/programmes/youth-capacity-fund#section-2">priorities and eligibility</a> above and ensure you show us how you meet these.</p>

                <div class="message">
                    <p>We would encourage you to submit via our online form, even if your group or partnership is in the early stages of development. We can discuss timescales for completing the full application with you,  what information you will need in order to complete it and what support is available for you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-box u-inner-wide-only accent--{{ pageAccent }} a--border-top">
            <div class="u-constrained-wide s-prose accent-content--{{ pageAccent }}">

                <h2>Questions you'll be asked</h2>

                <p>{{ printButton('Print these questions', metrics = true) }}</p>

                {{ questionsPreview(form.steps, copy) }}

                {{ startButton(startUrl) }}

                <h2>After your application is submitted</h2>

                <p>If your request is successful, your local funding team will contact you and give you a full application form to fill out and return to us.</p>
                <p>A first round of decisions will be made in December 2018. Groups will be given more time if they have a great idea but are not ready to provide information needed for a full grant assessment. Final decisions may be made until April 2019.</p>

            </div>
        </div>


    </main>
{% endblock %}
